Samburu Woman Representative Maison Leshoomo has called upon the nation to support President Uhuru Kenyatta and the handshake with Opposition Chief Raila Odinga. Leshoomo says the building bridges initiative was birthed to unite Kenyans in the aftermath of the divisive 2017 general elections. She was speaking at Kenyatta stadium in Maralal town after distributing funds, water tanks and bee hives to women and youth self help groups.